      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''During the day the people, the police and the army are with the government, but during the night, the people, the police and the army are all with the Taliban and Al Qaeda.''</p>
        <p>HAJI SAIFULLAH, a shopkeeper in Tirin Kot, Afghanistan. [A12]</p>
